{"tid":845892,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"如果我話思覺老師先係第一代youtuber同KOL，有沒人不認同？","createTime":"2018-10-03T04:39:50.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-03T11:36:23.000Z","uid":154872,"like":56,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"bbe12fc6b3844e15139b506d005bfd767ce2a39f","tid":845892,"uid":154872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T04:39:50.000Z","msg":"先不提思覺老師文筆，簡直驚天地泣鬼神，思路跳脫，文理清晰。<br />\n<br />\n思覺老師拍ge短片，差不多每段都會同觀眾互動，喺未有live stream的年代，已經好難得。<br />\n<br />\n其次短片內容往往發人深省，諷刺時弊，幽默輕鬆，拎出來睇都高汁過好多youtuber！<br />\n<br />\n仲係痴線佬始祖，要知道當時上網barrier 十分高，思覺老師仍然排除萬難同一眾信徒為大家帶來歡樂。<br />\n<br />\n所以我話：乜乜達仔，司徒夾帶，hayhay，以至馬車，龍心......諸如此類<br />\n<br />\n全部都唔夠思覺老師高汁同原創性高！"},{"pid":"b2452470964a184c7a31b3f6193bac80ba60bc43","tid":845892,"uid":154872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T04:43:34.000Z","msg":"是不是沒人識思覺老師了？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b07a7ad845e215d938ea9a3159e70c7af76cc0b4","tid":845892,"uid":3994,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T04:43:55.000Z","msg":"走得太前"},{"pid":"d11397e79c2229477f4c89828028638470bb7293","tid":845892,"uid":154872,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b07a7ad845e215d938ea9a3159e70c7af76cc0b4","tid":845892,"uid":3994,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T04:43:55.000Z","msg":"走得太前"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T04:50:46.000Z","msg":"如果遲10年出世會不會成為亞洲最佳youtuber<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94fff04dca19d45d1594e5a878d76e4ce9e722f1","tid":845892,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T04:51:36.000Z","msg":"新聞組<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"139b49068c8700b88832cf691e426fa64ae54f21","tid":845892,"uid":31841,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"b2452470964a184c7a31b3f6193bac80ba60bc43","tid":845892,"uid":154872,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"